card_name: Neighborly Complaints
description: The next inspection takes 3 additional ticks.

card_name: Economic Downturn
description: All permit and inspection times increase by 2 ticks for the next 3 turns.

card_name: New Safety Regulations
description: All players must discard 1 Expeditor card. All inspections take 3 additional ticks this turn.

card_name: Labor Strike
description: All construction times increase by 4 ticks for the next 2 turns.

card_name: Positive Press
description: The current high-profile client filing takes 3 ticks less time. Draw 1 Expeditor Card.

card_name: Unexpected Archeological Find
description: If a filing involves excavation increase its time by 6 ticks.

card_name: Zoning Variance Required
description: The current filing takes 4 ticks more time. Draw 1 Expeditor Card.

card_name: Materials Shortage
description: All players' current construction phase takes 3 ticks more time.

card_name: NIMBY Lawsuit
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project is high-profile; increase the current filing time by 5 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: City Council Allies
description: The current permit filing takes 2 ticks less time. Draw 1 Expeditor Card.

card_name: Holiday Rush
description: All filing times increase by 2 ticks this turn.

card_name: Soil Contamination
description: If the current project involves groundwork increase the filing time by 4 ticks.

card_name: Endangered Species Habitat
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project is in a designated habitat area; increase the permit filing time by 6 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: Funding Delay
description: Skip your next turn.

card_name: Annexation
description: The current filing takes 5 ticks more time but the player's next turn takes 2 ticks less time.
turn_effect: Next turn: reduce time by 2 ticks

card_name: Expeditor Lobbying
description: The next inspection takes 2 ticks less time. Discard 1 Expeditor card.

card_name: Neighborhood Revitalization
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project is in a targeted revitalization area; reduce the permit filing time by 3 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: Bribery Scandal
description: All permit filing times increase by 2 ticks for the next 3 turns.

card_name: Planning Department Backlog
description: The current filing takes 3 ticks more time.

card_name: Building Code Update
description: All inspection times increase by 2 ticks for the next 2 turns.

card_name: High-Profile Client
description: The current filing time is reduced by 4 ticks. All other players' current filing time increases by 1 tick.

card_name: Economic Boom
description: All construction times decrease by 2 ticks for the next 3 turns.

card_name: Project Redesign
description: The current filing is delayed indefinitely. Discard 2 Expeditor cards.

card_name: Expeditor Conference
description: Skip this turn. Draw 2 Expeditor Cards.

card_name: Celebrity Endorsement
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project is high-profile; reduce the permit filing time by 4 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: Community Outreach
description: All permit filing times decrease by 1 tick this turn.

card_name: Permit Office Upgrade
description: All players' current filing times decrease by 2 ticks.

card_name: Surprise Inspection
description: The next inspection takes 4 ticks more time.

card_name: Utility Delay
description: If the project requires utility hookups increase the filing time by 3 ticks.

card_name: Cybersecurity Breach
description: All filing times increase by 1 tick for the next 2 turns.

card_name: Permit Fee Hike
description: The current permit filing costs 2 extra resources but takes 2 ticks less time.

card_name: Diversity Initiative
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project team is diverse; reduce the inspection time by 2 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: Worksite Injury
description: All construction times increase by 3 ticks this turn.

card_name: Natural Disaster
description: All filing and inspection times increase by 4 ticks for the next 2 turns.

card_name: Expeditor Quits
description: Skip your next turn. Discard 2 Expeditor cards.

card_name: City Budget Surplus
description: All permit filing times decrease by 2 ticks this turn.

card_name: Affordable Housing Initiative
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project includes affordable housing; reduce the permit filing time by 5 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: Intern Error
description: The current filing time increases by 2 ticks.

card_name: Rezoning Request
description: The current filing time increases by 3 ticks. Draw 1 Expeditor Card.

card_name: Historical Preservation
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project involves a historic building; increase the filing time by 4 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: Competing Projects
description: Ask each other player about their current worktypes. If any player has the same worktype as you increase your filing time by 2 ticks.

card_name: Sister City Collaboration
description: All players' current filing times decrease by 1 tick.

card_name: Green Building Bonus
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the project is LEED certified; reduce the total filing time by 3 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: State Funding
description: The current high-profile project filing time is reduced by 4 ticks.

card_name: Mayor's Pet Project
description: Roll a die. On 1-3 the mayor expresses interest in the project; reduce its filing time by 5 ticks. On 4-6 no effect.

card_name: Expeditor Awards
description: The player with the most completed projects reduces their current filing time by 4 ticks.

card_name: Political Gridlock
description: All filing times increase by 1 tick for the next 5 turns.

card_name: Graft Investigation
description: All permit filings are halted for 1 turn while players discard half their Expeditor cards.

card_name: Permitting Process Overhaul
description: All filing times are reduced by 2 ticks for the remainder of the game. Each player draws 1 Expeditor Card.
